        <b>Races:</b>&nbsp; Humans, Iksar<br>
        <b>Stats:</b>&nbsp;  15 AC +100 HP +10 AGI +20 STR +10 DEX +10 STA +10 SV COLD +10 SV DISEASE +10 SV FIRE +10 SV MAGIC +10 SV POISON<br>
        <b>Special Attributes:</b>&nbsp; MAGIC, NO DROP, LORE<br>
        <b>Slot(s):</b>&nbsp; Hands<br>
        <b>Weight:</b>&nbsp; 0.1 Stone<br>
        <b>Effect:</b>&nbsp; Celestial Tranquility        &nbsp;</td>
