	   </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' bgcolor='#ebd8c3' class='db'><span class='spti'>Miscellaneous Information</span><br>
        <b>Rarity:</b> Very Rare<br>
<b>Proc Level:</b>&nbsp; 50<br>
<b>Effect Details:</b>&nbsp; This effect provides the Monk Wielder with a 40% haste buff, 52 ATK and 12 AC.  It is self only and has no cast time when activated.  The durations is however only 9 seconds and will not stack with enchanter haste buffs making it almost useless on any grouped raid.  Wielding these gloves automatically makes hand based damage 9/16.<br>
      </td>
